Resource Profile: Imaging Study

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/arkhn/arkhn-ig-osiris/StructureDefinition/onco-imagingstudy Version: 2.1.0
Draft as of 2024-05-13 Computable Name: OncoImagingStudy

Description of an imaging study.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Connection with the imaging module, Radiomics Image Filters and ROI segmentation
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-ct, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-dx, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-mri-2, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-mri and ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-pt-nm

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
